DESCRIPTION:<p dir="ltr">Join us for an in-depth livestream tailored for de
 velopers\, where we unveil the techniques behind NVIDIA NeMo Retriever’s in
 dustry-leading performance in enterprise retrieval-augmented generation (RA
 G) applications. Discover how NeMo Retriever secured first-place across the
  ViDoRe V1\, ViDoRe V2\, and MTEB Visual Document Retrieval leaderboards us
 ing NVIDIA’s winning techniques. </p><p dir="ltr">Learn how to use NVIDIA A
 I Blueprints like AI-Q for building AI agents and RAG\, to build world-clas
 s multimodal retrieval systems. We’ll cover leaderboard-winning techniques\
 , real-world integration strategies\, and best practices for deploying scal
 able\, production-ready RAG systems that set a new standard for enterprise 
 AI.</p>\nJoin us on either: \n\nYouTube: <a href="https://www.youtube.com/w
 atch?v=GJ6RmhGrQdA&ab_channel=NVIDIADeveloper">https://www.youtube.com/watc
 h?v=GJ6RmhGrQdA&ab_channel=NVIDIADeveloper</a>\n\nLinkedIn: <a href="https:
 //www.linkedin.com/events/7349505027461304320/comments/">https://www.linked
 in.com/events/7349505027461304320/comments/</a>\n\nX: <a href="https://x.co
 m/NVIDIAAIDev">https://x.com/NVIDIAAIDev</a>\n\nJoin our discord: <a href="
 https://discord.gg/nvidiadeveloper">https://discord.gg/nvidiadeveloper</a>\
 n\nSee you there!
LAST-MODIFIED:20260402T153203Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:(NVIDIA Live) Top-Ranked RAG: NeMo Retriever Leads Visual Document 
 Retrieval Leaderboards
TRANSP:OPAQUE
