ATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;CN=t.meye
 r@99ads.com;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:t.meyer@99ads.com
ATTENDEE;CUTYPE=INDIVIDUAL;ROLE=REQ-PARTICIPANT;PARTSTAT=ACCEPTED;CN=suport
 eluccamagnata@gmail.com;X-NUM-GUESTS=0:mailto:suporteluccamagnata@gmail.com
X-GOOGLE-CONFERENCE:https://meet.google.com/xmc-cehx-guf
CREATED:20260402T033656Z
DESCRIPTION:Event Name: 99ads Interview with Tara\n\nI am absolutely thrill
 ed to meet with you and talk about our available role at 99ads. This interv
 iew is all about you - your experience\, your goals and if this role is bes
 t suited for you.\n\n\nI am looking forward to the call!\n\nLocation: This 
 is a Google Meet web conference.\nYou can join this meeting from your compu
 ter\, tablet\, or smartphone.\nhttps://calendly.com/events/05564d96-d655-48
 8c-bdfd-1d4e05216024/google_meet\n\nPlease share anything that will help pr
 epare for our meeting.:\nHi 99ads Team\nI am applying for the Creative Stra
 tegist position. I operate at the intersection of performance data and dire
 ct response creative.\nYou are looking for someone who understands Meta and
  TikTok for DTC brands. I recently led the creative strategy for a wellness
  DTC brand on cold traffic. We abandoned standard transformation claims and
  used identity recognition hooks instead. This pivot achieved a 34 percent 
 Hook Rate and a 4.55x ROAS.\nYou also need a leader who can write briefs an
 d guide editors. I build automated creative intelligence pipelines. I use n
 8n to scrape TikTok and the Meta Ads Library. This system automatically gen
 erates fully researched creative briefs. This infrastructure reduced our cr
 eative testing cycle from 14 days down to 7 days. I translate cold data int
 o precise direction so the creative team knows exactly what to build.\nI do
 cumented my entire methodology online. You can see my DTC case studies and 
 the exact breakdown of my automated briefing architecture in my portfolio h
 ere:\n<a href="https://calendly.com/url?q=https%3A%2F%2Fluccacreativestrate
 gist.netlify.app%2F&user_uuid=43bde60b-df35-453b-8222-fbacf6ce3e63&stage=0&
 hmac=391b58f24b267c07491d9ebe5a8d171925aa807f448a2859e7d6aa7664ed1e43">http
 s://luccacreativestrategist.netlify.app/</a>\nI look forward to discussing 
 how we can implement these frameworks for your client roster.\nBest regards
 \nLucca Magnata\n\nRole you're applying for.: Creative Strategist\n\nWhere 
 did you hear about the role?: Tara Meyer\n\nNeed to make changes to this ev
 ent?\nCancel: https://calendly.com/cancellations/6ef33580-8dc4-493e-ae4d-1c
 0144296b23\nReschedule: https://calendly.com/reschedulings/6ef33580-8dc4-49
 3e-ae4d-1c0144296b23\n\nPowered by Calendly.com\n\n\nEntrar com o Google Me
 et: https://meet.google.com/xmc-cehx-guf\nOu disque: (ZA) +27 10 823 0355 P
 IN: 493942635#\nMais números de telefone: https://tel.meet/xmc-cehx-guf?pin
 =9661301699358&hs=7\n\nSaiba mais sobre o Meet em: https://support.google.c
 om/a/users/answer/9282720
LAST-MODIFIED:20260402T043557Z
LOCATION:Google Meet (instructions in description)
